[41:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'copy selected constraints. And I\'ll choose damp track and copy rotation and press okay. Now the selected bones kept their copy location constraint, but on top of that,'

[41:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
