[54:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'like the one we had in level two. So in edit mode I\'ll select the root bone, shift D, duplicate it and move it on the Z axis. Scale it down.'

[55:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
