[209:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'rename some of these bones, but for now, if there are no 001s in your names, you\'re good to go. So, step two, go to edit mode. Select all bones, and definitely disable'

[210:05] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the X axis mirror, or you may mess up some of these asymmetrical bones. Press Shift D, and then right click to cancel the movement. Now, you have a perfect copy'

[210:19] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'of your deforming bones, and they are all conveniently selected. So, let\'s use that. Press M, make a new collection, and I\'ll call it DEF2. Okay, so now we have these two DEF'

[210:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'collections with identical bones. Now, one of these two sets of identical bones will become the actual deform bones, and the other set will act as a connection. A connection between the'

[210:48] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
