[213:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'I\'m going to enable the connective collection, and so I want the target for its constraint to be the pelvis bone. In other words, we want to give all of'

[213:41] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the deforming bones a copy transforms constraint. The target will be the armature, and I want to set the bone field to a bone with the same name, but without a DEF prefix.'

[213:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
