[214:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'constraints, set a copy transforms constraint, set target to the armature, and do not set the bone yet. Press A to select all other bones, go to pose,'

[214:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'constraints, copy constraints to selected bones. Now, all bones will have the copy transforms with the armature set as target and we only have to set up the bone.'

[214:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
