[215:10] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'constraints will be the name of the bone itself minus DEF- So, for DEF pelvis, it will be just pelvis. For DEF spine one, it will be just spine'

[215:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'one and so on. So, let\'s set it up here. This will be pelvis. Spine one, spine two, and so on and so'

[215:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'forth. Let\'s do it. &gt;&gt; Okay, it took me about 8 minutes, not'

