VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'easier weight painting, as you\'ll see in the weight painting chapter, which will come after that. And the final benefit will mainly affect those of you who plan to work with game engines or export your'

[220:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'character to other 3D applications. And it is that we can now parent these deforming bones in any way we like, which is super important when exporting'

[220:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the rig because it will ensure a clean export of the rig, and it can also be important for compatibility with your game engine. To understand what I mean,'

[221:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
