[221:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'connection between these bones is an absolute mess. It only works because of the connection to the connective bones through copy transforms. But that is okay. It simply means that we can have'

[221:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'absolutely any hierarchy we want in these deform bones. So, for example, I could go to edit mode, select all of them, press Alt P, and clear the parent. Now, all of these bones are completely'

[221:54] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'disconnected from each other and from the rest of the rig, but if I enable copy transforms again, I\'ll select all bones, activate the constraint on the active'

[222:06] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
