[222:19] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'hierarchy of these deform bones do not matter. Now, what I would recommend is to parent the deform bones in a logical hierarchy. This will be ideal for most game engines and other applications. So,'

[222:31] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'if you have no plans of working with other applications, you can actually skip this step, but I would recommend it. Let\'s go to edit mode. And I\'ll want to parent the head to the'

[222:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
