[222:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'P. And to make my work easier, I can right click on keep offset and add it to my quick favorites. Now, I can just press Q and choose keep offset. Select the next two bones. Q'

[223:08] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'keep offset. The next two keep offset. Keep offset. Keep offset. Let\'s parent both shoulders to this chest bone. Keep offset.'

[223:20] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
