[229:02] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'need one prefix. So, I\'ll rename this bone, and I\'ll just remove the m c h part. And same for the lower arm. d e f lower arm.l'

[229:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'And that\'s it for the deform bones. Now, we\'ll go over the remaining collections and check if the bones there are m c h or controls.'

[229:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
