[237:48] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'left arm IK. Click create. And I\'ll hide the new collection. Next, I\'ll select these three bones. They are all I need to animate this arm'

[238:01] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'in FK mode. So, I\'ll create a new bone collection, call it left arm FK, and create. So, that is what I meant when I said that we\'ll separate the bones based on'

