VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'by dragging and dropping them into the control collection. Okay, so even though the control'

[241:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'collection does not contain anything, if I disable its visibility, it will automatically disable all sub collections. We could also create sub sub collections. So, technically, we could'

[242:11] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
