[242:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'we\'ll keep it simple and just use these sub collections under the control collection. And as a final tweak to the collections, I\'ll select the control collection and use the arrows to place it at the top'

[242:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and the DEF at the bottom. This is optional, and also optionally, I\'ll organize my MCH layers a little bit. I\'ll press Alt H to unhide everything, and I\'ll split the MCH bones into MCH'

[242:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'IK, MCH FK, MCH twists, and other bones. This will make your work easier if you decide to tweak any of the mechanisms. The main goal is to be able to easily'

[243:02] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'hide and unhide bones that are meant for a specific mechanism. You don\'t need to follow this part very precisely or at all. It\'s kind of optional. So, it\'s going to be a time lapse, and you can'

[243:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'try to do more or less what I\'m doing, or just do the kind of organization that makes sense to you. &gt;&gt; I\'m done organizing, so I\'m going to'

