VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Okay, I\'ll press Alt H and enable X-ray'

[252:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'to see what other bones I need to set up here. I\'ll set up the finger controls next. Select all of them on both hands. Set custom object to WGT finger.'

[252:48] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Right click, copy to selected. And that gives us these Rigify looking finger controls. For the torso,'

[253:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
