[263:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'screen. Then set the active color to this hex value. Once you set up the first set, you can place the mouse over the selected color, press control C, and then move the mouse'

[263:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'over the selected of the next set, and press control V, and keep doing that for all sets. Next, copy the active color of the first'

[263:41] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'set, and paste it into the other sets. Okay, now the presets will be updated.'

[263:55] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
