[264:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'left side, and give them the blue color. And now let\'s select the right side,'

[265:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and give them the red color. The root will be purple. And for settings, I can use another'

[265:23] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
