[313:10] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Now this should look fine.'

[313:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'But you can experiment with setting this weight to 0.75 or so and painting this area with this weight. So the neck bone will get a weight of'

[313:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: '0.75 here, which means that the chest bone will get 0.25. And I think this is looking good.'

[313:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
