[317:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'there\'s some intersection here, so let\'s try to fix that. The shoulder does not have any influence over the shirt here, so that\'s why that happens. So, let\'s just paint lightly for both shoulders.'

[318:10] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'And do some smoothing. Distribute the weights and smooth until'

[318:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it\'s fixed. Let\'s try to remove all weights from the'

[319:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
