[368:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'control the effect of your driver. And what we did is the simplest way of affecting this graph. We just move the end point up and down, which is more or less the same as multiplying the expression by something.'

[368:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'You can add additional points here and make your driver act non-linearly. For now, I\'ll just make you aware of this and we\'ll see we might have the'

