[368:58] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'with drivers, we are now unable to control this bone manually, which in this case is kind of fine. You can also apply the automation plus parent technique to avoid this. But let\'s check out the other solutions to this problem'

[369:11] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
