[378:32] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'then I have to move the bone further up to trigger the entire animation. Let\'s say I\'m happy with this. I\'ll select all bones, shift select the one that has the constraint, go to pose, constraints, copy constraints.'

[378:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'And now moving this bone up triggers the animation for all bones. Now, the AC animation is still active, which is not necessary and also not desirable because if I go through the timeline, the'

