AUDIO: 'animation will play, which I don\'t want. I just want to trigger the animation using this control bone. So, let\'s just unlink the animation. Now, it won\'t play, but the constraint will still work. And'

[379:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'something really cool about the action constraint is that even though these bones are constrained and they\'re performing a very complex movement, I can still move them freely at any point. And that\'s why I said that the action'

[379:27] [scene:talk]
